load_with

Load each OpenGL symbol using a custom load function. This allows for the use of functions like glfwGetProcAddress or SDL_GL_GetProcAddress. ~~~ignore gl::load_with(|s| glfw.get_proc_address(s)); ~~~

Search Tricks

Prefix searches with a type followed by a colon (e.g. fn:) to restrict the search to a given type.

Accepted types are: fn, mod, struct, enum, trait, type, macro, and const.
